node.text:
Giveaway time! We’re so excited for fall adventures that we are giving away THREE of the new Disney Baby @MobyWrap featuring Winnie the Pooh! For your chance to win:

1️⃣ Follow @DisneyBaby
2️⃣ Comment your favorite Winnie the Pooh character
3️⃣ And use the hashtag #DisneyBabySeptemberWrapSweepstakes in your comment!

Good luck! Don’t forget – this is the only official account that will contact our sweepstakes winners! NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Ends 9/20/21 at 11:59 PM PT. Open to 50 US/DC; 18+. Void where prohibited. One entry per person. Rules/odds: http://di.sn/6008y4hiC
